high_descs: Walk to the microwave above the sink.
Pick up the egg in the microwave.
Walk to the sink on the left.
Rinse the egg in the sink and then pick the clean egg up.
Turn around and walk to the white table with the coffee machine on it.
Place the egg in front of the wine glass on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg in front of the wine glass on the white table.

high_descs: Walk slightly to the right to the microwave.
Open the microwave and take out the egg on the right, then close the microwave.
Walk slightly to the left to the left sink basin.
Put the egg in the left sink basin, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn around and walk forward to the dining table.
Put the egg on the dining table, to the left and in front of the bottle of soap.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg on a dining table.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of you
Pick up an egg from the microwave
Move to the sink ahead of you
Clean the egg in the sink
Move to the table behind you
Put the egg on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg on the table across from the sink.
